room_title: Escape room "Taken" by Aiken 2 Escape in Aiken
room_description: The rain was coming down hard, and you could hardly see out of your windows as you and your friends were driving down Highway 1. You were on edge listening to your friend recollect stories of all the missing women who disappeared along this stretch. Suddenly, you hear a loud pop and realize your tire has blown. The last thing you remember is the glare of the headlights as you stepped out of your car and the sound of footsteps approaching...now you and your team must escape the cold, dark basement youâ€™ve been taken to before the footsteps return!
